The paper proposes a new statistic for dimensionality reduction and data analysis, which is a fundamental tool in machine learning and data science. The paper also discusses the application of this statistic in various settings such as weather data, soundscape data, and dynamical systems data. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.IT (Information Theory), and cs.NA (Numerical Analysis).
